{"title":"短诗三首","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":11,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"短诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说姑娘直往城里跑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说姑娘不爱庄稼汉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘听得直冒火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝汽灯底下瞧一眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里蹲着个小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支着脖子在发楞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“在想啥呀？你！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘心里骂了一声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你干吗不站起来辩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就听凭这富农瞎胡编？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘急得脸一红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起手要求发言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（写在双槐树）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辩论会上\t朱城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一次又一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘟哝着说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“钱有花了之日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有见面之时。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别瞧他那副熊像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一肚子尽是坏水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他到底想跟谁见面？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别放松，紧跟着追！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底该是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向我们认罪低头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是该我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再向这个地主下跪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散会\t朱城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会散了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在沉思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在低语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在继续辩论。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这块土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又扎进了几寸深？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（于京郊西平庄）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}